The paper discusses the use of artificial neural networks (ANNs) for forecasting indoor temperature in a house, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on energy efficiency and the integration of technologies in a house also suggests the categories of sustainable development (cs.SD) and computer engineering (cs.CE). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of a complex monitoring system, which could fall under the category of software engineering (cs.SE).
